//! Cross-compatibility: a vault + sync blob sealed by the **Dart** mobile app
//! (`mobile.dart/tool/gen_fixture.dart`) must open in `threefa_core`. Together
//! with the mirror test on the Dart side, this proves the two implementations are
//! byte-compatible in both directions, so accounts sync across desktop and mobile.

